<apex:page standardController="Opportunity"
           renderAs="pdf"
           showHeader="false"
           applyBodyTag="false"
           applyHtmlTag="false">

<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .section {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .signature {
            margin-top: 60px;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        td {
            padding: 6px;
        }
        .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            width: 40%;
        }
        .box {
            border: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="title">
    VEHICLE LOAN AGREEMENT
</div>

<div class="section">
This Loan Agreement ("Agreement") is made on the date of execution between:
</div>

<div class="section box">
<b>Lender:</b> ABC Finance Limited<br/>
<b>Borrower:</b> {!Opportunity.Name}
</div>

<div class="section">
WHEREAS the Borrower has requested financial assistance for the purchase of a vehicle, and the Lender has agreed to grant such assistance subject to the terms and conditions contained herein.
</div>

<div class="section">
<h3>Loan Details</h3>
<table border="1">
<tr>
    <td class="label">Sanctioned Loan Amount</td>
    <td>₹ {!Opportunity.Eligible_Loan_Amount__c}</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td class="label">Interest Rate (Annual)</td>
    <td>{!Opportunity.Interest_Rate__c}%</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td class="label">Loan Tenure</td>
    <td>{!Opportunity.Loan_Tenure_Months__c} Months</td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td class="label">Monthly EMI</td>
    <td>₹ {!Opportunity.EMI_Amount__c}</td>
</tr>
</table>
</div>

<div class="section">
<h3>Terms &amp; Conditions</h3>

1. The Borrower agrees to repay the sanctioned loan amount along with applicable interest through monthly instalments (EMIs) as specified above.  
2. The Borrower shall ensure timely payment of each EMI on or before the due date.  
3. Any delay in payment may attract penal interest as per lender policy.  
4. The loan shall be secured against the financed vehicle until full repayment.  
5. The Borrower confirms that all information provided during assessment is true and accurate.  
6. The Lender reserves the right to initiate recovery proceedings in case of default.  
</div>

<div class="section">
<h3>Declaration</h3>
The Borrower hereby declares that he/she has read, understood, and agreed to all terms and conditions mentioned in this Agreement.
</div>

<div class="signature">
<table>
<tr>
    <td>
        ___________________________<br/>
        Borrower Signature
    </td>
    <td style="text-align:right;">
        ___________________________<br/>
        Authorized Signatory<br/>
        ABC Finance Limited
    </td>
</tr>
</table>
</div>

<div class="section" style="margin-top:40px; font-size:10px;">
This is a system-generated document and does not require physical signature unless mandated by regulatory compliance.
</div>

</body>
</html>

</apex:page>